80,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩睇完，其實都ok既，不過拍得太短，呢個題材拍長啲說故事可以好啲，依家套戲兩個鐘都唔夠搞到後面勁急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪明顯係小說續集？"},{"pid":"d7a04077f028f7ab960ba71468e1e2f5392e9a81","tid":380380,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"一見到編劇有Akiva Goldsman份就知套野無運行"},{"pid":"36f9a9806cfd36dc22aa6b837ee738a64b45aec7","tid":380380,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩睇完，其實都ok既，不過拍得太短，呢個題材拍長啲說故事可以好啲，依家套戲兩個鐘都唔夠搞到後面勁急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪明顯係小說續集？</blockquote><br />\n無睇過小說,唔識答<br />\n不過套戲節奏掌控得太差<br />\n但套戲個結尾都適合開到續集,如果電影公司戰勝到呢套戲既負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b266498331e9bc86d07f7caf799b4c23a42c356","tid":380380,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"好似得9x mins?會唔會太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e823d7cd2d73690b39c9170d6d7121f18bf096eb","tid":380380,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似得9x mins?會唔會太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺,即係調返轉marvel啲戲如果拍到呢個時間佢地都仆街啦<br />\n唔知慳黎做咩"},{"pid":"d86d531b63a70699345225769c2aafb493012ff1","tid":380380,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似得9x mins?會唔會太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺,即係調返轉marvel啲戲如果拍到呢個時間佢地都仆街啦<br />\n唔知慳黎做咩</blockquote><br />\n本身想睇<br />\n但見到咁短<br />\n覺得會揸流灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d472553d7f3de41a7e08df5dd63b1344ce6c4a8","tid":380380,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩睇完，其實都ok既，不過拍得太短，呢個題材拍長啲說故事可以好啲，依家套戲兩個鐘都唔夠搞到後面勁急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪明顯係小說續集？</blockquote><br />\n無睇過小說,唔識答<br />\n不過套戲節奏掌控得太差<br />\n但套戲個結尾都適合開到續集,如果電影公司戰勝到呢套戲既負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話會出劇"},{"pid":"a104d82463072569a55e2ea6f4c5330804525843","tid":380380,"uid":44113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"最後入度門寫住Hong Kong Palace<br />\nGoogle 咗係中菜館嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解jack chamber 唔可以用shine 造成物理攻擊？<br />\n<br />\nGun stainer(唔知係咪咁串）係識背首野就當係定點 因為最後Roland 對jack 講 gun stainer <br />\n但係應該係血脈嚟 因為Roland 身體異於常人又可以長壽<br />\n成套戲交代太少<br />\n竟然用.45 殺到個大佬<br />\n咁地球嘅火力都唔會怕外星怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個tower 都未入過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 滿心期待"},{"pid":"a9129bc0a2f0c38d432426ab391843816ab42469","tid":380380,"uid":36403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:13:24.000Z","msg":"套戲交代背景太少，最後又收工mode <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2488a440a54ba3214e1af2e42a68c6593790b6b0","tid":380380,"uid":41705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"又驚中伏但係又想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce22aca5d0eae5f88b9c775ede585ccc8f9aa3a","tid":380380,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"Matthew型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d765ea8e60163414f11cc21be0b2a6693911fe16","tid":380380,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-